//Friends
@61012 = ~Wand of Friends~
@61013 = ~This wand will temporarily grant 6 points of Charisma to the wielder. Those who view the affected tend to be very impressed with <PRO_HIMHER> and make an effort to be <PRO_HISHER> friends and help <PRO_HIMHER>, as appropriate to the situation. Officious bureaucrats might decide to become helpful; surly gate guards might wax informative; attacking orcs might spare the caster's life, taking <PRO_HIMHER> captive instead.

